---
<Base title="GitHub Trending Top 10 (Apr 24, 2026) — Alishahryar1/free-claude-code Leads" description="Daily GitHub Trending Top 10 for 2026-04-24, with concise analysis and highlights.">

<article class="post">
  <header>
    <span class="tag">🔥 Trending</span>
    <h1>GitHub Trending Top 10 (Apr 24, 2026)</h1>
